Moskowitz v. Power et al. Louis J. Lefkowitz, Attorney General of New York, Samuel Hirshowitz, First Assistant Attorney General, and Philip Kahaner and Robert S. Hammer, Assistant Attorneys General, for respondents Power et al., and Joseph Slavin and Eugene Victor for respondent Lerner, in opposition.
